1.00	Hearts_Grown_Brutal	Hearts Grown Brutal	Hearts Grown Brutal: Sagas of Sarajevo is a non-fiction book by New York Times reporter Roger Cohen chronicling his experiences covering the Bosnian War and the Bosnian Genocide. Random House published the book on August 25, 1998. The book won a Citation for Excellence from the Overseas Press Club in 1999.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/7e/Hearts_Grown_Brutal.jpg
